{
  "texts": [
    "Despite the plethora of existing definitions of what RAI should entail, given our investigations we conclude that:",
    "• RAI should be value-sensitive.",
    "Learning from the field of Value-Sensitive Design Friedman et al. (2002), RAI should consider the values and priorities of key stakeholders who own, use, and are affected by these systems.",
    "These values should guide the system design from the outset.",
    "• RAI should be inclusive and participatory."
  ]
}